name: Ohio Toxic Release Inventory, 2007 EPA
description: This is a dataset of Ohio's TRIS (Toxic Release Inventory) reported to the EPA for the year 2007. Data was pivoted to get sums of emissions data as well as company names based on latitude and longitude. This was then uploaded into Geocommons as a csv.
